<title>GERMANY: SAP breaks out costs for H1 1997.</title>
<headline>SAP breaks out costs for H1 1997.</headline>
<dateline>FRANKFURT 1997-07-24</dateline>
<text>
<p>Costs for the six months ending June 30 (in millions of marks unless stated):</p>
<p>				    H297    pct of   H296   pct of</p>
<p>						sales	     sales</p>
<p>    Total costs		1,895     78.9   1,271    79.8</p>
<p>of which:</p>
<p>     personel costs	    913     38.0     589    37.0</p>
<p>     service costs	     248     10.3     166    10.4</p>
<p>     charges			89	3.7	76     4.8</p>
<p>     other/taxes		 645     26.9     440    27.6</p>
<p>    Number of employees    6-30-97	    6-30-96</p>
<p>				   11,084		7,766</p>
<p>NOTE - Full name of the German software group is SAP AG .</p>
<p>-- Bonn Newsroom, +49-228 26097150</p>
